{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Employing staff for the first time"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/employing-staff.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/employing-staff"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B680","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"The main things you need to consider when hiring an employee for the first time or if you've never hired an employee before","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:12:43+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>There are 5 things you need to do when employing staff for the first time.</p>\n</div>\n\n<ol class=\"steps\">\n<li><p><strong>Decide how much you need to pay someone:</strong> you must pay your employee at least the <a href=\"/your-right-to-minimum-wage\" title=\"the National Minimum Wage\">National Minimum Wage (<abbr title=\"National Minimum Wage\">NMW</abbr>)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Check if someone can legally work for you:</strong> you need to check if they have the <a href=\"/legal-right-to-work-in-the-uk\" title=\"Legal right to work in the UK tool\">legal right to work in the UK</a>. You may have to do other employment <a href=\"/checks-on-job-applicants\" title=\"checks on job applicants\">checks</a> as well.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Get employment insurance:</strong> you need employers\u2019 liability insurance as soon as you become an employer. It must cover you for at least \u00a35 million and come from an <a href=\"http://www.fsa.gov.uk/register/home.do\" title=\"find an authorised insurer\" rel=\"external\">\u2018authorised insurer\u2019</a> - you can find one online.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Register with HM Revenue &amp; Customs (<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>) and pay your employee:</strong> you need to <a href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/paye/intro/register.htm\" title=\"Register as an employer\" rel=\"external\">register as an employer,</a> make any <a href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/paye/payroll/day-to-day/paying.htm\" title=\"Deductions\" rel=\"external\">deductions</a> (ie <abbr title=\"Pay As You Earn\">PAYE</abbr> and National Insurance contributions (<abbr title=\"National Insurance Contributions\">NICs</abbr>)) and give a <a href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/paye/payroll/day-to-day/paying.htm#2\" title=\"Pay statement\" rel=\"external\">pay statement</a> to your employee.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong>Send details of the job (including terms and conditions) in writing to your employee:</strong>  if you\u2019re employing someone for more than a month, you need to give them a <a href=\"/employment-contracts-and-conditions/written-statement-of-employment-particulars\" title=\"Written statement of employment particulars\">written statement of employment</a> within their first 2 months.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/Employing_People_files/Written_Statement.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Template for a written statement of employment (PDF, 628KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download \u2018Template for a written statement of employment\u2019 (PDF, 628KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Read the <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> booklet below for advice on taking on your first employee. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/employers/employing-someone.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Thinking of employing someone?' (PDF, 541KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download \u2018Thinking of employing someone?\u2019 (PDF, 541KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Recruiting and hiring","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/employing-people%2Frecruiting-hiring.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes discrimination law, apprenticeships and using agencies","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=employing-people%2Frecruiting-hiring","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/employing-people/recruiting-hiring"},"parent":{"title":"Employing people","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/employing-people.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes pay, contracts and hiring","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=employing-people","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/employing-people"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"National Minimum Wage rates","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/national-minimum-wage-rates.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/national-minimum-wage-rates","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"1859","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Employment contracts","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/employment-contracts-and-conditions.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/employment-contracts-and-conditions","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"352","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Check if someone can work in the UK","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/legal-right-to-work-in-the-uk.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/legal-right-to-work-in-the-uk","format":"smart-answer","details":{"need_id":"B91","business_proposition":false}}]]],"parts":null}